@startuml
title Workflow: Document Baseline → SRS Suggestions

|#AntiqueWhite|Document Owner|
start
:Create/Approve baseline;
:Submit to SRS Agent;

|#LightBlue|Baseline Engine|
:Parse baseline doc;
:Extract requirements;
:Map to SRS impact matrix;
:Generate SRS suggestions;

|#LightGreen|SRS Owner|
:Review suggestions;
if (Accept?) then (yes)
  :Update SRS;
  :Commit to version control;
else (no)
  :Reject with reason;
endif

|#LightYellow|Notification|
:Notify Document Owner of status;

stop
@enduml
